#. addon summary
msgid "invisinote"
msgstr "invisinote"

#. addon description
msgid ""
"Browse notes virtually from configured folders.\n"
"\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+P: open path\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+P: open settings (configure folders and file types)\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+[: previous folder\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+]: next folder\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+N: load notes\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+U: previous note\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+O: next note\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+I: previous line\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+K: next line\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+J: previous word\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+L: next word\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+,: previous character\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+.: next character\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+A: read note\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+A: copy note\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+;: copy line\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+I: select to previous line\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+K: select to next line\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+J: select to previous word\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+L: select to next word\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+,: select to previous character\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+.: select to next character\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+;: copy selection\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+BACKSPACE: clear selection\n"
msgstr ""
"從設定的資料夾中虛擬瀏覽檔案。\n"
"\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+P：開啟路徑\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+P：開啟設定（設定資料夾與檔案類型）\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+[：上一個資料夾\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+]：下一個資料夾\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+N：載入檔案\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+U：上一個檔案\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+O：下一個檔案\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+I：上一行\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+K：下一行\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+J：上一個單字\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+L：下一個單字\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+,：上一個字元\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+.：下一個字元\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+A：朗讀檔案\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+A：複製檔案\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+;：複製行\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+I：選取至上一行\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+K：選取至下一行\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+J：選取至上一個單字\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+L：選取至下一個單字\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+,：選取至上一個字元\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+.：選取至下一個字元\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+SHIFT+;：複製選取內容\n"
"- NVDA+ALT+BACKSPACE：清除選取\n"

